readable.content: A group of people are rowing a boat in a contest . A rowing team races forward in competition with the motivation of their leader in front of the boat . Boat number 5 has several men with life jackets paddling the water . People in orange vests are rowing with great effort . Several people are rowing a boat while being cheered on by a person with a drum
